d by the grantee from the direct costs it charges to the grant. ( Authority: 20 U.S.C. 1221e&hyph;3(a)(1), 2831(a), 2974(b), and 3474) [FR Doc. 94&hyph;905 Filed 1&hyph;13&hyph;94; 8:45 am] BILLING CODE 4000&hyph;01&hyph;P
